Description.value:
This iFlow sends the changes on the customer and address level to the SAP ERP system. It collects first all events with the changes. The current customer and address data will be sent to the ERP system. 
If the customer has an ERP customer number, the data of the corresponding customer will be updated in the ERP system.
If the customer has no ERP customer number, a new number will be generated and a new customer will be created on the ERP system. It is also possible to influence the number generation by defining a number assignment range on the ERP system.
Deletion of the customer is not supported.
